OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1774264485
OL,3,CWimbledon Tennis Championships to
OL,4,Cintroduce video reviews
OL,6,FBut that has not stopped organisers
OL,7,Fgiving the green light to more
OL,8,Ftechnology, with players in singles
OL,9,Fmatches on the six show courts
OL,10,Fpermitted to challenge certain calls
OL,11,Fmade by umpires, for example on
OL,12,Fwhether a ball has bounced twice or if
OL,13,Fa player has touched or leaned across
OL,14,Fthe net.
OL,16,FThe new technology will be introduced
OL,17,Fon Centre Court, No.1 Court, No.2
OL,18,FCourt, No.3 Court, Court 12 and Court
OL,19,F18.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/4
